Document.document: Add "-N" flag to force double quotes around identifiers. This is the default, but the new flag will allow overriding an alias, for example. So psql -n -N will put in the double quotes, and psql -n can be an alias for psql. Also, add a few braces around a nested single-line conditional construct to suppress compiler warnings about "an ambiguous else".
